<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Garden & Plants Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your stylesheet for styling -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .product {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .product-item {
            width: 48%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .product-item img {
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .product-item h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .product-item p {
            font-size: 1em;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Garden & Plants Blog</h1>
            <p>Your source for gardening products, tips, and inspiration</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="plants">
            <h2>Plants</h2>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600?text=Healthy+Plants" alt="Healthy Plants">
            <p>Explore the best plants for your garden and how to care for them. From indoor plants to outdoor greens, learn how to grow a variety of plants in different climates. Here are some products that will help you grow a lush and vibrant garden.</p>
            <div class="product">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Indoor+Plant" alt="Indoor Plant">
                    <h4>Indoor Plant Starter Kit</h4>
                    <p>Everything you need to grow your indoor plants successfully. Includes pots, soil, and a variety of plants to get started.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Outdoor+Plant" alt="Outdoor Plant">
                    <h4>Outdoor Garden Plants</h4>
                    <p>High-quality plants for your garden. Choose from a variety of flowers, shrubs, and trees to beautify your outdoor space.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="seeds">
            <h2>Seeds</h2>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600?text=Garden+Seeds" alt="Garden Seeds">
            <p>Starting a garden from seeds is a rewarding experience. Learn how to properly plant and care for seeds to ensure they grow into healthy plants. Here are some great seed kits to get you started!</p>
            <div class="product">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Vegetable+Seeds" alt="Vegetable Seeds">
                    <h4>Organic Vegetable Seed Kit</h4>
                    <p>A variety of vegetable seeds, perfect for your home garden. Includes heirloom tomatoes, cucumbers, and carrots.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Flower+Seeds" alt="Flower Seeds">
                    <h4>Wildflower Seed Mix</h4>
                    <p>Brighten your garden with a mix of wildflowers. This seed mix will attract pollinators like bees and butterflies!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="gardens">
            <h2>Gardens</h2>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600?text=Beautiful+Garden" alt="Beautiful Garden">
            <p>Design and create your dream garden with ideas and inspiration. Learn about different garden styles, landscaping tips, and how to maintain a thriving garden. Check out these garden essentials!</p>
            <div class="product">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Garden+Tools" alt="Garden Tools">
                    <h4>Complete Garden Tools Set</h4>
                    <p>All the essential tools for your garden. From pruning shears to shovels, this set will make your gardening easier.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Garden+Fertilizer" alt="Garden Fertilizer">
                    <h4>Organic Garden Fertilizer</h4>
                    <p>Boost your garden's health with this all-natural fertilizer. Perfect for flowers, vegetables, and plants.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="fruits">
            <h2>Fruits</h2>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600?text=Fruit+Trees" alt="Fruit Trees">
            <p>Growing fruits at home can be a fun and rewarding hobby. Discover how to grow fruit trees, bushes, and vines in your backyard or garden. Here are some of our top picks!</p>
            <div class="product">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Fruit+Tree" alt="Fruit Tree">
                    <h4>Fruit Tree Starter Kit</h4>
                    <p>Includes everything you need to start growing fruit trees. Choose from apples, peaches, or pears!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Berry+Bush" alt="Berry Bush">
                    <h4>Berry Bush Kit</h4>
                    <p>Grow your own berries with this simple starter kit. Includes blueberry, raspberry, and strawberry bushes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="flowers">
            <h2>Flowers</h2>
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600?text=Flower+Garden" alt="Flower Garden">
            <p>Flowers bring color and beauty to any garden. Find out how to grow beautiful flowers, from perennials to annuals, and how to keep them healthy throughout the seasons. These flower products will help you bloom!</p>
            <div class="product">
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Flower+Seeds" alt="Flower Seeds">
                    <h4>Flowering Plant Seeds</h4>
                    <p>Start your flower garden with a mix of annual and perennial flowers. Brighten up your space with these easy-to-grow seeds.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-item">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300?text=Flower+Pots" alt="Flower Pots">
                    <h4>Decorative Flower Pots</h4>
                    <p>These beautifully designed flower pots are perfect for displaying your blooming flowers on patios or windowsills.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Garden & Plants Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
